00:35:43.992 --> 00:35:46.354
<i>We'll cook through the
weekend if necessary.</i>

505
00:35:46.378 --> 00:35:51.530
We will have 400 pounds
for you by next week.

506
00:35:54.853 --> 00:35:56.831
I have your word on that?

507
00:35:56.855 --> 00:36:00.390
You do. You have
my word on that.

508
00:36:01.626 --> 00:36:03.926
<i>Thank you for the update.</i>

509
00:36:24.615 --> 00:36:28.300
Yeah. Right.

510
00:36:30.672 --> 00:36:32.416
Any news?

511
00:36:32.440 --> 00:36:36.437
No. I'm just... Just wandering.

512
00:36:36.461 --> 00:36:38.356
How's everybody doing?

513
00:36:38.380 --> 00:36:41.993
Uh. well. as well
as can be expected.

514
00:36:42.017 --> 00:36:45.229
It's this not knowing.

515
00:36:45.253 --> 00:36:47.687
that's the hardest
part. I think.

516
00:36:48.991 --> 00:36:51.669
Anything new on these guys?

517
00:36:51.693 --> 00:36:53.838
Who they are? What they wanted?

518
00:36:53.862 --> 00:36:57.697
No. nothing yet.
but we'll get it.

519
00:37:01.803 --> 00:37:03.636
Steve...

520
00:37:05.573 --> 00:37:09.604
Do you think there
could maybe be others?

521
00:37:09.628 --> 00:37:12.907
Buddy. nobody's getting to Hank.

522
00:37:12.931 --> 00:37:15.342
That was their one
shot and they blew it.

523
00:37:15.366 --> 00:37:18.579
So no.

524
00:37:18.603 --> 00:37:20.748
No way.

525
00:37:20.772 --> 00:37:23.218
Jesus.

526
00:37:23.242 --> 00:37:24.652
I'd love to walk in there

527
00:37:24.676 --> 00:37:26.955
and shoot that bastard
right in the head.

528
00:37:26.979 --> 00:37:28.528
Me too.

529
00:37:36.688 --> 00:37:38.983
Yeah?

530
00:37:39.007 --> 00:37:40.417
Oh. yeah?

531
00:37:40.441 --> 00:37:43.120
Great. We'll be right down.

532
00:37:43.144 --> 00:37:44.588
Food's here.

533
00:37:44.612 --> 00:37:46.757
Hey. you like Pollos Hermanos?

534
00:37:46.781 --> 00:37:49.861
You guys coming? - Yeah.

535
00:37:49.885 --> 00:37:51.428
Um. on occasion. yeah.

536
00:37:51.452 --> 00:37:53.130
Owner's a big
booster for the DEA.

537
00:37:53.154 --> 00:37:54.298
He heard what happened.

538
00:37:54.322 --> 00:37:56.906
He's gonna feed every
cop in the building.

539
00:37:58.142 --> 00:38:00.655
That's... That's
wonderful. Yeah.

540
00:38:00.679 --> 00:38:03.580
And. apparently. he's
bringing it by personally.

541
00:38:11.789 --> 00:38:13.600
I don't even know what to say.

542
00:38:13.624 --> 00:38:15.303
That's an incredible...

543
00:38:15.327 --> 00:38:18.139
Good. huh? Delicious.

544
00:38:18.163 --> 00:38:21.208
That's so generous of
you. Thank you very much.

545
00:38:21.232 --> 00:38:23.744
Yes. thank you. Guys.
did you hear that?

546
00:38:23.768 --> 00:38:26.630
Mr. Fring is offering
a 10.000-dollar reward

547
00:38:26.654 --> 00:38:28.833
on any information
about the case.

548
00:38:28.857 --> 00:38:32.770
Well. that's...
That's wonderful.

549
00:38:32.794 --> 00:38:34.989
Wow. thank you. Mr. Fring.

550
00:38:35.013 --> 00:38:37.792
You're very welcome.
Men like your husband

551
00:38:37.816 --> 00:38:40.711
are the thin blue line
between us and these animals.

552
00:38:40.735 --> 00:38:42.234
I only wish I could do more.

553
00:38:47.943 --> 00:38:50.087
Well. we do
appreciate your support.

554
00:38:50.111 --> 00:38:55.259
This reward could turn
the tide here. It'll really help.

555
00:38:55.283 --> 00:38:58.796
Again. I can't express
how sorry I am.

556
00:38:58.820 --> 00:39:01.966
As it happens. I actually
met Agent Schrader.

557
00:39:01.990 --> 00:39:03.367
Really?

558
00:39:03.391 --> 00:39:05.569
Our fund run.
couple of months ago.

559
00:39:05.593 --> 00:39:09.840
Mr. Fring was one
of our sponsors.

560
00:39:09.864 --> 00:39:13.677
I. uh. talked for a few
minutes with your husband.

561
00:39:13.701 --> 00:39:18.271
As a matter of fact.
Mr. White. your name came up.

562
00:39:20.275 --> 00:39:22.753
Really? Heh.

563
00:39:22.777 --> 00:39:26.757
Yeah. there happened to
be a collection jar out for you.

564
00:39:26.781 --> 00:39:29.727
and we spoke briefly
about your health concerns.

565
00:39:29.751 --> 00:39:33.981
I hope that there's
been good news.

566
00:39:34.005 --> 00:39:35.616
Uh...

567
00:39:35.640 --> 00:39:37.985
Things have improved. yes.

568
00:39:38.009 --> 00:39:40.404
That's wonderful to hear.

569
00:39:40.428 --> 00:39:43.879
It was clear to me how
deeply he cares for you.

570
00:39:45.933 --> 00:39:50.198
Well. I have taken up
enough of your time.

571
00:39:50.222 --> 00:39:54.285
Um... Thank you again very much.

572
00:39:54.309 --> 00:39:56.103
It was a great
pleasure to meet you.

573
00:39:56.127 --> 00:39:58.211
Thank you. WALT
JR.: Yes. thank you.

574
00:40:00.148 --> 00:40:03.415
Let me walk you out.
Oh. no. it's not necessary.

575
00:40:05.953 --> 00:40:07.593
It's amazing.

576
00:40:09.190 --> 00:40:12.370
You know. I didn't
say thank you.

577
00:40:12.394 --> 00:40:16.028
I'll walk him out.
Be right back.

578
00:40:18.633 --> 00:40:21.045
Good to see you.
Enjoy the chicken?

579
00:40:21.069 --> 00:40:23.914
Good. Good. Excuse me.

580
00:40:23.938 --> 00:40:27.451
Uh... My pleasure. My pleasure.

581
00:40:27.475 --> 00:40:29.186
Thank you. Thank you.

582
00:40:29.210 --> 00:40:31.188
It's good chicken.
huh? Good. Yeah.

583
00:40:31.212 --> 00:40:33.524
Mr. Fring. I. uh... Mr. White.

584
00:40:33.548 --> 00:40:35.225
I just wanted to
thank you again.

585
00:40:35.249 --> 00:40:36.961
It's my pleasure.

586
00:40:36.985 --> 00:40:41.054
Uh. may I...? May I speak
with you? Just a moment.

587
00:40:45.426 --> 00:40:47.638
You knew. You...

588
00:40:47.662 --> 00:40:51.508
You knew my brother-in-law
was with the DEA.

589
00:40:51.532 --> 00:40:54.645
I investigate everyone
with whom I do business.

590
00:40:54.669 --> 00:40:57.531
What careful man wouldn't?

591
00:40:57.555 --> 00:41:02.442
He is not a problem
for us. for our business.

592
00:41:07.415 --> 00:41:08.680
Your being here is...

593
00:41:09.934 --> 00:41:12.246
Is this some sort of message?

594
00:41:12.270 --> 00:41:14.782
I'm supporting my community.

595
00:41:14.806 --> 00:41:17.652
I hide in plain
sight. same as you.

596
00:41:17.676 --> 00:41:19.287
Are we done?
No. listen. I. uh...

597
00:41:19.311 --> 00:41:21.205
This attack on
my brother-in-law.

598
00:41:21.229 --> 00:41:23.207
I don't... I don't
understand it.

599
00:41:23.231 --> 00:41:25.293
I don't know what it means.

600
00:41:25.317 --> 00:41:29.563
Please. if you have
some knowledge

601
00:41:29.587 --> 00:41:31.788
that you could share with me...

602
00:41:36.311 --> 00:41:38.956
I fear for my family.

603
00:41:38.980 --> 00:41:40.358
I'm sure they'll be fine.

604
00:41:40.382 --> 00:41:44.262
I am told the assassin that
survived is gravely injured.

605
00:41:44.286 --> 00:41:47.169
It's doubtful he'll live.

606
00:41:50.575 --> 00:41:53.459
Now thank me and shake my hand.

607
00:41:56.664 --> 00:42:01.050
Thank you. Thank you again.
You're quite welcome. Mr. White.

608
00:42:02.720 --> 00:42:05.532
Did you hear that?

609
00:42:09.361 --> 00:42:11.873
We're going up? MAN: Come on.

610
00:42:11.897 --> 00:42:14.575
What's going on?

611
00:42:14.599 --> 00:42:16.711
What's happening?

612
00:42:16.735 --> 00:42:20.581
Starting chest compressions.
One. two. three. four.

613
00:42:20.605 --> 00:42:22.282
One. two. three... NURSE: Defib?

614
00:42:22.306 --> 00:42:24.034
No reason. Patient
is in asystole.

615
00:42:24.058 --> 00:42:25.953
Continuing chest compressions.

616
00:42:25.977 --> 00:42:27.438
One. two. three. four.

617
00:42:27.462 --> 00:42:30.307
Give me a liter of saline.
I can't get a pulse back.

618
00:42:30.331 --> 00:42:31.775
One. two. three. four.

619
00:42:31.799 --> 00:42:33.010
Still nothing.

620
00:42:33.034 --> 00:42:35.313
All right. stopping
compressions.

621
00:42:35.337 --> 00:42:37.648
Time? Eight forty-three.

622
00:42:37.672 --> 00:42:39.867
Time of death. 20:43.

623
00:42:41.793 --> 00:42:45.177
Burn in hell. you piece of shit.

624
00:43:10.839 --> 00:43:12.683
Yes? Juan?

625
00:43:12.707 --> 00:43:14.585
<i>I assume you heard the news.</i>

626
00:43:14.609 --> 00:43:17.421
Your man died. I heard.

627
00:43:17.445 --> 00:43:20.241
It's unfortunate.
<i>Yeah. unfortunate.</i>

628
00:43:20.265 --> 00:43:23.244
And meanwhile. I have
Federales surrounding my house.

629
00:43:23.268 --> 00:43:27.130
You know what I think. Gustavo?
I think you're behind all this.

630
00:43:27.154 --> 00:43:29.432
Why would I do this?

631
00:43:29.456 --> 00:43:30.668
How would it serve me?

632
00:43:30.692 --> 00:43:32.920
That's the part I'm
trying to figure out.

633
00:43:32.944 --> 00:43:35.339
Go off on your own. maybe.

634
00:43:35.363 --> 00:43:37.491
Would you actually
think that would work?

635
00:43:37.515 --> 00:43:39.994
<i>You sound like you're
under a lot of stress.</i>

636
00:43:40.018 --> 00:43:41.429
<i>Maybe you should call me back</i>

637
00:43:41.453 --> 00:43:43.598
when you're seeing
things more clearly.

638
00:43:43.622 --> 00:43:45.365
I see things clear enough.

639
00:43:45.389 --> 00:43:49.136
One DEA gets shot. all of
Washington starts barking.

640
00:43:49.160 --> 00:43:51.439
The D.F. suddenly has
to put on a big show.

641
00:43:51.463 --> 00:43:54.374
<i>and I wind up with
Federales in my rosebushes.</i>

642
00:43:54.398 --> 00:43:56.193
<i>But just for a while.</i>

643
00:43:56.217 --> 00:44:00.664
Appearances. politics.

644
00:44:00.688 --> 00:44:02.566
<i>Are you still there. Gustavo?</i>

645
00:44:02.590 --> 00:44:04.568
Yes.

646
00:44:04.592 --> 00:44:06.704
I'm here.

647
00:44:06.728 --> 00:44:08.623
<i>I'll weather this. I always do.</i>

648
00:44:08.647 --> 00:44:10.290
My brother's a police chief.

649
00:44:10.314 --> 00:44:13.127
I got connections.
They'll get me through.

650
00:44:13.151 --> 00:44:15.496
And when I get proof.

651
00:44:15.520 --> 00:44:18.833
and the others find
out what you've done.

652
00:44:18.857 --> 00:44:22.419
maybe we come pay you
a visit. Maybe we can...

653
00:45:11.025 --> 00:45:15.772
Skyler. Skyler. Marie. Marie.

654
00:45:15.796 --> 00:45:18.475
Oh. how is he? Tell
me something good.

655
00:45:18.499 --> 00:45:21.946
I think he's stable enough
now for you to go see him briefly.

656
00:45:21.970 --> 00:45:24.648
I'm sorry. I'm afraid it's
immediate family only.

657
00:45:24.672 --> 00:45:26.717
We're all family. I understand.

658
00:45:26.741 --> 00:45:29.419
But we have a certain
protocol here that we need...

659
00:45:29.443 --> 00:45:32.828
We're all family.

659
00:45:33.305 --> 00:46:33.632
